name: SXZ Hero Picker
description:
This hypernetwork was trained on Warcraft 3 Reforged Units and Heroes portraits on AbyssOrangeMix2_sfw with clip skip 2.

Keep hypernetwork strength about 0.6 for decent results. Best results you may get with square images, but another aspect ratio also supported.

See my prompt examples in showcase generation info.

Please share your images in review section down below.
